text:
This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report.   

Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: 

This point in time. This time. No time. All the time. Any time. Out of time. In The Current Moment. The Defining Moment. Any moment now. Now or never. This moment. A Pivotal moment.
title: June 23, 2020: A PIVOTAL MOMENT
